Date:   1/19/12
Author: Matt Davison

This coding exercise is an Accordion widget implemented in Javascript.  The widget does not use JQuery.  
The code uses AJAX to access a server-side PHP script that provides the current date and time.

Files:

accodionwdidget.html -- HTML and JavaScript code
styles.css           -- CSS code
dateandtime.php      -- PHP script for getting date and time
arrow-down.png       -- image
arrow-right.png      -- image
